Text.string: How's that Jakobs resistance thing goin'? They're lucky to have you on board.
I guess Wainwright wasn't wrong to call Aurelia a harpy all those times.
Those Calypsos sure get around, huh? What's next, gettin' buddy-buddy with the saurians?
Wish I coulda been there when you took Aurelia down. Nice one.
Oh, man... I can't believe they got Tannis. This is bad.
Whatever they're planning on doin' with Tannis, we gotta stop 'em.
How did Tannis keep this under wraps for so long? That's crazy.
This is the big one, Vault Hunter. You ready for it?
Pandora will never be safe as long as those Calypsos are still around. You gotta take 'em out.
Hah. Adios, Troy. Pendejo.
How the hell is Typhon still alive after all these years? Dude's gotta be like... a million.
So, the lost planet of Nekrotafeyo, huh? Can't be weirder than Pandora, right?
Heard about Typhon and the Calypsos. Man, that's one messed up family.
Sure hope that space machine does what it's supposed to do.
Pandora's our home. We gotta protect it no matter what.
Not gonna lie. Things have been getting pretty wild around here.
Bummed I didn't get to meet Typhon. I bet that dude had some crazy stories.
I've seen the Destroyer. If Tyreen's got that kinda power... Hope you're ready for a hell of a fight.
You saved the planet and killed the friggin' Destroyer? I'm glad I'm on your side, Vault Hunter.
Lilith. I... I think she's still out there. I dunno. Maybe by now I've just convinced myself nothing could kill her. Even teleporting a freakin' moon.
The B-Team's always ready to back up the Crimson Raiders. No matter what happens.
B-Team! You see this logo? That's good branding, ese.
Man, being back on Pandora again brings up some bad memories. Bloodwing. Jack. This whole plant-monster thing. I was almost a plant once—you know that?
I kept telling people that one of these days, the bandits would rise up and take over Pandora, but no one listens to me. It's 'cause of the goatee, isn't it?
Before Talon, I had a bird named Bloodwing, but Handsome Jack killed her. Anyone comes near Talon, they get a bullet to the brain from three-hundred yards.
Lilith's opened a contract with us to do missions for the Crimson Raiders. Feels good to be back.
I always got my eyes on the horizon.
Feels like a million years ago I first stepped foot on Pandora. Can't tell if things are totally different or exactly the same.
I've tried dating again, but Brick and Tina always scare 'em off. It's like being the youngest child all over again.
Tina's always after me to play that game again with her. Tch, I ain't got time for that. I'm WAY into tactical miniatures these days.
Zer0 and I had the snipe-off of the century a while back. Winner got the other's rifle. Maybe I'll give it back to him someday, heh-heh-heh.
Oh, I could SO go for a soda right now.
Talon, she's lovin' being back on Pandora. The bandits she's been chasin' for sport? Ha! They're not lovin' it so much.
Did I ever tell you about the time I almost turned into a plant? I wonder what I would have been. Maybe, like... a cool willow tree.
Haven't done a good old-fashioned prison break since my first month on Pandora.
Troy was bad enough before he had powers. Now he's just insufferable. And I thought Jack was a dick.
With a dad like that, you'd think the Calypsos woulda turned out better.
Oh, man... Typhon got killed by his own daughter? All the more reason to put her down, I guess.
I guess it's over. I wonder if Lilith's okay.
Kill anything big and bad lately?
Rifle's gettin' dirty. Think it's time for a good cleanin'.
I wish there was an easier way to get blood out of my clothes. These are gettin' kinda crusty.
Don't worry too much about puttin' down bandits. They'd eat you as soon as look at you.
Woof. I picked the wrong decade to quit drinking.
Feels like I could learn a thing or two from that Clay guy.
Warring AI's, huh? Sounds like a trip.
We've been doing mercenary work for a few years, but never messed around with that Rogue-Sight stuff. Looks freaky. I wanna know I can trust my eyes, comprende?
You killed ANOTHER Vault monster? Holy crap, you're unstoppable.
It's kind of amazing what a bunch of bandits can do when they actually set their mind to somethin', huh?
How was that little road trip through the scar? Sounded exciting.
Troy got exactly what was comin' to him. Good work.
The freakin' legend himself, Typhon DeLeon. Can't believe it.
Need a gig? I got one.
I got a mission for ya.
Hey, badass. Got a job for you.
Hey. S'up.
Yo, Vault Hunter.
Hey there.
Oh, hey.
Look at this badass.
Damn, it's bright. Hardly saw ya, Vault Hunter.
What's up, Vault Hunter? Damn, it's bright.
Evenin', Vault Hunter.
I saw you comin' in the dark. Night vision, baby.
Hey, nice sniper. I like your style.
That rifle's lookin' mighty sweet, my friend.
Got somethin' for ya.
Lookin' to get into trouble?
Wanna help me with somethin'?
Things are gonna go down.
Got time for somethin'?
Estas occupado or what, Vault Hunter?
You still on that thing, Vault Hunter?
How's it going, Vault Hunter?
Let me know when you're done with that thing.
Everything cool, man?
Yeah, later.
See ya.
Catch you later.
Don't be a stranger.
Good hunting.
Later!
Hasta pronto, Vault Hunter.
Hope you don't get killed.
See ya, amigo.
Be careful out there.
